description:
Why is life so hard? Why am I here? Why was I born? What’s the solution to the mess we’re in? If we’re so smart, why haven’t we been able to solve these problems by now? 

Finding satisfying answers to these questions is important because the answers determine our identity, affect our happiness, and influence how we treat ourselves and others. Confusion over these questions can lead to hopelessness and suicide. Why is life so hard? Does the Bible offer an acceptable answer? What does the Bible teach about our position in the universe that can offer a sense of belonging and purpose?

Learn why only the Word of God can offer satisfying solutions to life’s biggest questions.
